  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/b1f11cda8219717acef55572bdedd1cc.webp?t=1622123672\" width=640 height=61 /></span><br><br><strong>Broken Sky</strong> is a fast paced dogfighting shooter featuring unlockable planes, weapons and special abilities. <br><br>Arcade action from the start. No boring, long winded missions - just fly, shoot and kill as many aliens as you can.<br>Use resource points to equip your plane however you want and go into battle against the alien hordes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/dee169fa87f6e61946c45d75f644861b.poster.avif?t=1622123672\" width=546 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/dee169fa87f6e61946c45d75f644861b.webm?t=1622123672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/dee169fa87f6e61946c45d75f644861b.mp4?t=1622123672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Super fast air combat</strong> with responsive controls and explosive weapons.<br></li><li> 6 Different plane types.<br></li><li> 6 primary weapons, 6 secondary weapons and 4 specials.<br></li><li> All <strong>weapons are interchangeable</strong> depending on Plane Resource Points.<br></li><li> Wander around the Pilots bunker and log-in to the terminals.<br></li><li> <strong>23 different achievements</strong> based on Survival time, Kills and Missions flown.<br></li><li> <strong>30+ random bonus challenges</strong> to complete.<br></li><li> 14+ different enemy types.<br></li><li> Loads of <strong>Steam Achievements</strong> to unlock.<br></li><li> <strong>Steam Leaderboards</strong> - Can you make it to the top?!<br></li><li> plus loads of crashes, abductions and massive explosions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/45586ced3dc3677783ba5f4cfccae8e6.poster.avif?t=1622123672\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/45586ced3dc3677783ba5f4cfccae8e6.webm?t=1622123672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439970/extras/45586ced3dc3677783ba5f4cfccae8e6.mp4?t=1622123672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
